highPerformanceModels1.title: Oxygen Generator
highPerformanceModels1.name: Oxygen Generator 80 HP

specifications.tagline: Costeeffective, safe and convenient oxygen generator for your business

highPerformanceModels1.description: The robust build, reliability and low maintenance make our oxygen generators suitable for extreme environments, such as gold mining. While a specially designed muffler makes it one of the quietest PSA systems on the market.
highPerformanceModels1.advantages: But the advantages don’t end there. When a constant, onsite source of oxygen is available not only are cyanide reactions affected but energy consumption can be reduced. And the additional oxygen removes nitrogen entrainments present in the air.
highPerformanceModels1.content: Oxair’s oxygen generator can also be engineered to integrate with any existing system, or designed from scratch.
